# Optional — enables silent, in-page contact form delivery (no backend needed).
#
#   1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io  (~1 minute)
#   2. Copy your endpoint, e.g.  https://formspree.io/f/abcdwxyz
#   3. Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`), paste the endpoint below, rebuild.
#
# If left empty, the form falls back to opening the visitor's email app,
# prefilled with their message — so it still works with zero setup.

VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
